context: Tonsillectomy and adenoidectomy. McIvor mouth gag was placed in the oral cavity, and a tongue depressor applied.   (Medical Transcription Sample Report)
Using the radiofrequency wand, the tonsils were ablated bilaterally.
The adenoid tissue was fulgurated with the suction Bovie set at 35.
